EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 2100Z DAILY
   18 THRU 24 JUL IN AREA WITHIN
   32 MILES OF 57-15.9N 008-28.1W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA

   ON VHF CH 16 OR PHONE: 187 060 4449
   FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 242200Z JUL 17.
